  • Constructor Details

    • Variant

      Variant​(int alleleId, java.lang.String type, int position, int pathogenicity, int geneId, java.lang.String alternateAllele, java.lang.String disease, java.lang.String referenceAllele, java.lang.String chromosome)
      Constructor for a Variant object.
      Parameters:
      alleleId - - int - The Allele ID of the Variant SNP.
      type - - String - What type of SNP.
      position - - int - The position on the chromosome that the SNP is located.
      pathogenicity - - int - whether the SNP is believed to be pathogenic. 1 for pathogenic, 0 for nonpathogenic or uncertain.
      geneId - - int - The ID of the gene that the SNP is located on.
      alternateAllele - - String - The alternate allele that is causing the SNP
      disease - - String - The disease that the SNP is causing
      referenceAllele - - String - The allele that is found on the same position as the alternate allele but in the reference genome
      chromosome - - String - The chromosome the SNP is located on.
